## 1. Install [jupyter_to_medium](https://www.dexplo.org/jupyter_to_medium/) on Jupyter:


```python
!pip install jupyter_to_medium
!jupyter bundlerextension enable --py jupyter_to_medium._bundler --sys-prefix
```

 

## 2. Get your integration token:

Get your integration token by going to your [Medium Account's Settings](https://medium.com/me/settings) > Integration Token.

 

## 3. Set your integration token:


```python
!mkdir ~/.jupyter_to_medium # create folder
!echo "YOUR-INTEGRATION-TOKEN" > ~/.jupyter_to_medium/integration_token # add integration token
```

All done!

The next time you restart Jupyter Notebook, you will be able to deploy your notebooks straight to Medium!
